00:00:34.718 --> 00:00:37.286
there is a power named kundalini

00:00:37.847 --> 00:00:40.329
and this power on getting awakened

00:00:41.033 --> 00:00:43.501
you can get your self realisation.

00:00:44.302 --> 00:00:45.898
This I will say certainly that

00:00:46.315 --> 00:00:49.252
very clearly whole outline

