in many scriptures as well

00:01:01.902 --> 00:01:04.668
it has very clearly been mentioned.

00:01:07.060 --> 00:01:12.176
Don't know why do we  consider

00:01:14.527 --> 00:01:17.871
knowledge from foreign countries

00:01:18.490 --> 00:01:20.973
as the best

00:01:21.316 --> 00:01:26.520
and our any asset in this country

00:01:26.949 --> 00:01:28.049
give it least importance

00:01:28.926 --> 00:01:30.654
don't know its importance.

00:01:31.103 --> 00:01:35.233
Its reason may be is that we were under slavery for such a long time

00:01:35.449 --> 00:01:39.485
and we were overwhelmed by these people because they were ruling us.

00:01:42.297 --> 00:01:45.223
Now that we are free

00:01:45.933 --> 00:01:48.427
in that freedom we should observe

00:01:48.742 --> 00:01:51.046
what are our assests

00:01:51.111 --> 00:01:53.911
what is our history

00:01:54.247 --> 00:01:59.238
and what did we discover?

00:01:59.999 --> 00:02:05.795
India is such a unique country where

00:02:06.841 --> 00:02:12.997
man has  less problems of the outside world

00:02:13.208 --> 00:02:15.397
For example, if in London you have to go out of your home

00:02:15.734 --> 00:02:18.964
at least for fifteen, twenty minutes you have to dress up yourself

00:02:19.165 --> 00:02:20.628
then you can go out.

00:02:21.134 --> 00:02:24.614
In our country too there are so many places

00:02:26.306 --> 00:02:29.701
for example, Himalayas or at high altitudes

00:02:29.902 --> 00:02:33.450
where it is very cold, people don't live there.

00:02:34.306 --> 00:02:39.195
But I have seen in these countries that the problems

00:02:40.529 --> 00:02:47.291
quarelling with everyone all the time go on troubling them so much

00:02:47.878 --> 00:02:52.871
that they are fully lost in that.

00:02:53.262 --> 00:02:57.422
But in India the climate is so good that we sit in open.

00:02:58.592 --> 00:03:01.004
In Russia also you cannot sit in the open.

00:03:01.540 --> 00:03:04.673
In any country one cannot sit so much in the open.

00:03:04.931 --> 00:03:06.894
There used to sleep on the floor

00:03:07.095 --> 00:03:09.232
They said, Mother, many people will come to listen to your lecture

00:03:09.433 --> 00:03:10.487
there is no other place than a stadium.

00:03:10.644 --> 00:03:12.187
Stadium too was full to its capacity.

00:03:13.257 --> 00:03:16.003
So this characteristic of India that

00:03:16.204 --> 00:03:18.148
there is neither too much heat nor too cold

00:03:18.413 --> 00:03:22.240
and here at this place we didn't have to struggle against nature.

00:03:23.779 --> 00:03:30.755
So from eternity there were our ancestors.

00:03:30.956 --> 00:03:36.313
Those ancestors thought that finally our life is a daily affair.

00:03:36.514 --> 00:03:40.588
Daily we get crushed in our life.

00:03:40.789 --> 00:03:42.631
It has some or the other meaning.

00:03:43.066 --> 00:03:46.848
And because our climate was like that

00:03:47.049 --> 00:03:52.415
people definitely paid their attention more towards themselves

00:03:52.556 --> 00:03:55.426
than towards foreign countries.

00:03:56.020 --> 00:03:59.279
They didn't have any need to think about

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:01.065
the questions of outside topics

00:04:01.266 --> 00:04:02.650
how to find out a solution of those problems?

00:04:02.864 --> 00:04:04.302
They knew only this much that

00:04:04.503 --> 00:04:07.488
now everything boarding and lodging is almost okay.

00:04:07.566 --> 00:04:10.347
Even if you go into jungles, you can live in jungles too.

00:04:10.548 --> 00:04:12.881
There you can live by eating fruits and berries.

00:04:12.965 --> 00:04:15.387
This type of climate too

00:04:15.479 --> 00:04:21.176
we should say that God has blessed us specially of such a country.

00:04:21.615 --> 00:04:23.968
This country is a great country

00:04:24.169 --> 00:04:27.732
and there is a special blessing of God for this country

00:04:28.227 --> 00:04:31.587
and because of this blessing

00:04:32.025 --> 00:04:36.476
from eternity people of this country tried to find out

00:04:36.566 --> 00:04:39.639
why did we come in this world?

00:04:40.235 --> 00:04:44.947
And what for our life God has made?

00:04:45.148 --> 00:04:48.513
Why has He created us in the form of human beings?

00:04:49.302 --> 00:04:57.184
With this inspiration many people meditated in the jungles.

00:04:57.563 --> 00:05:01.062
They found out that our life has been created

00:05:01.375 --> 00:05:03.758
so that, we could go to the kingdom of God

00:05:04.563 --> 00:05:10.272
and their joy, and their love may be rewarded by that.

00:05:12.026 --> 00:05:17.439
God created the whole world and this universe.

00:05:17.528 --> 00:05:22.267
and after that left a human being from amoeba to this state

00:05:22.468 --> 00:05:26.189
and that only for the sake of being in that state of happiness

00:05:27.116 --> 00:05:32.005
that God's love and comfort we may be able to feel.

00:05:32.013 --> 00:05:34.976
So, God created this world.

