00:05:57.209 --> 00:06:01.501
and the beautiful picture of the world that he made

00:06:01.651 --> 00:06:05.228
that you can see today in sahajyoga.

00:06:06.199 --> 00:06:10.299
Whatever prophesy has been made, whatever has been said,

00:06:10.368 --> 00:06:13.322
whatever they desired by heart

00:06:13.523 --> 00:06:16.236
the time has come to be rewarded by success.

