Whatever you will come across, that is only just one thing

00:07:36.506 --> 00:07:40.088
what for is a man's life made?

00:07:40.289 --> 00:07:41.837
What is its meaning?

00:07:42.424 --> 00:07:43.882
Where has he to go?

