or go on depositing insurance policies

00:07:56.202 --> 00:07:58.034
or do some better work than this

00:07:58.235 --> 00:08:00.438
and grab the money of the whole world

00:08:01.188 --> 00:08:02.945
Is his life made for that?

00:08:03.853 --> 00:08:05.516
We should think

00:08:05.717 --> 00:08:09.066
Is our life made for such petty things?

