In this Punya Patnam, do all people eat only money?

00:08:29.970 --> 00:08:31.561
Has all bribery spread?

00:08:32.445 --> 00:08:33.814
Why has it happened?

00:08:34.033 --> 00:08:36.524
Why did we reduce ourselves to such a state?

00:08:36.645 --> 00:08:41.744
Because that which is desire within us to seek truth disappeared.

00:08:43.164 --> 00:08:46.409
We lost that desire, we are unable to understand that

00:08:46.805 --> 00:08:49.998
that we have to find out the truth

00:08:50.319 --> 00:08:52.888
Till we do not find out the truth

00:08:53.084 --> 00:08:56.215
till then we can never get solution.

00:08:56.355 --> 00:08:57.997
You become a millioner

00:08:58.083 --> 00:09:00.485
you eat lot of money , become a millioner

00:09:00.756 --> 00:09:04.124
but you can never get health.

00:09:04.369 --> 00:09:06.571
You can never get happiness.

00:09:06.772 --> 00:09:08.077
You cannot get love

