that any person may get tempted

00:09:22.243 --> 00:09:26.453
to bow his head to the photograph, however great he may be.

00:09:27.171 --> 00:09:30.511
We are the carriers of such a great culture.

00:09:30.764 --> 00:09:33.741
Having such a great culture

00:09:34.066 --> 00:09:37.844
Why have we gone down and now

00:09:37.961 --> 00:09:41.379
is there any way to escape is a separate question?

00:09:41.489 --> 00:09:45.094
If somebody asks Me, I will say that it is good in one way

00:09:45.295 --> 00:09:48.618
that it has at least created an illusion within us.

00:09:48.697 --> 00:09:51.646
We started thinking why did we fall like that?

00:09:52.370 --> 00:09:54.093
Why are we facing this plight

00:09:54.294 --> 00:09:57.257
and why are we doing it at a low level?

00:09:58.596 --> 00:09:59.596
Above all

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:07.217
when a man thinks what after this? After all why this?

00:10:07.331 --> 00:10:09.275
And then he becomes a seeker.

00:10:09.476 --> 00:10:11.736
And those who are seekers

00:10:11.990 --> 00:10:14.898
only he can get self realisation.

00:10:15.356 --> 00:10:18.114
and he who is not (a seeker) he may say anything

00:10:18.315 --> 00:10:20.783
however he may shout, he cannot get his self realisation.

00:10:21.128 --> 00:10:22.228
He is not a realised soul.

00:10:23.455 --> 00:10:26.305
Because when a person thinks in this direction,

00:10:26.506 --> 00:10:29.215
after all why did he come in this world?

00:10:29.457 --> 00:10:31.843
he points towards the truth

00:10:32.422 --> 00:10:35.100
and he wants to know the truth.

00:10:35.368 --> 00:10:38.728
I who am born as a human being, what is its importance?

00:10:38.939 --> 00:10:41.596
what is my status?

00:10:41.761 --> 00:10:45.287
To which level i am going?

00:10:45.418 --> 00:10:48.315
When a human being starts thinking all this

00:10:48.529 --> 00:10:50.494
he becomes a seeker.

00:10:50.701 --> 00:10:52.527
and when he becomes a seeker

00:10:52.724 --> 00:10:57.659
then for him, his kundalini, his own mother herself

00:10:57.677 --> 00:11:00.007
that is settled within him, gets enlightened in a sahaj way.

00:11:01.109 --> 00:11:04.749
In this case, in Russia I tell you, is so surprising

00:11:04.950 --> 00:11:09.096
that 14 Thousand and 16 thousand, there are also such people

00:11:09.299 --> 00:11:11.255
and all of them get realisation.

00:11:11.486 --> 00:11:14.868
I used to think that there they had never heard the name of God

00:11:15.048 --> 00:11:17.843
not knowing what is kundalini.

00:11:18.067 --> 00:11:19.568
Seeing just My photograph

00:11:19.769 --> 00:11:22.765
thousands of people came and got realisation.

00:11:23.058 --> 00:11:26.487
I observed that all their writers are

00:11:26.688 --> 00:11:32.064
too much in search of their inner mind, by introspection

00:11:32.337 --> 00:11:35.000
Their writers have shown that whatever work a man does

00:11:35.201 --> 00:11:37.300
always gropes for an answer.

00:11:37.502 --> 00:11:40.748
Why i do this? why i did this? what for i am doiing so?

00:11:40.949 --> 00:11:42.737
What is my intention?

00:11:43.530 --> 00:11:44.564
So,

00:11:45.741 --> 00:11:48.698
although in our country, people talk a lot about religion,

00:11:48.899 --> 00:11:49.969
have a great command on dharma

00:11:50.157 --> 00:11:54.546
and you have just seen that sadam sahib and  America

00:11:54.747 --> 00:11:58.135
has spoiled the show in the name of God, all the work

00:11:59.831 --> 00:12:02.020
quarrelling, create trouble

00:12:02.221 --> 00:12:04.537
kill this, kill that, supress everybody.

00:12:05.353 --> 00:12:07.228
All this is happening

00:12:07.429 --> 00:12:10.863
because a human being is not secured within himself.

00:12:11.616 --> 00:12:15.433
He doesn't know that God takes care of everybody's security

00:12:15.903 --> 00:12:17.050
But He loves everyone.

00:12:17.251 --> 00:12:20.691
Not only this, He is the Father of all fathers

00:12:21.715 --> 00:12:22.715
Absolute

00:12:24.935 --> 00:12:26.685
Ocean of mercy

00:12:27.085 --> 00:12:31.069
And we need not be insecured so much.

