And simply by My saying you may accept that thing, is not possible

00:12:35.586 --> 00:12:41.008
that I say that God's shelter is always spread over you.

00:12:42.352 --> 00:12:45.586
But you can surely feel it

00:12:45.793 --> 00:12:49.289
You can know it, in Marathi it is called ZANI.

