In Sanskrit it is called BODH

00:12:51.948 --> 00:12:54.356
or VIDH from which the word 'VED' has originated.

00:12:55.356 --> 00:12:58.724
The time has come that you can know it

00:12:58.925 --> 00:13:02.280
that it that God's grace is spread all around us.

00:13:03.584 --> 00:13:08.632
And when we get this power, then only

00:13:09.246 --> 00:13:11.053
In fact

00:13:11.254 --> 00:13:13.292
your yoga takes place.

00:13:13.691 --> 00:13:17.117
Before that, to talk about yoga, to stand on your head

00:13:17.318 --> 00:13:19.735
and to break your bones is not yoga.

00:13:20.872 --> 00:13:23.467
And people made yogas of different types.

00:13:24.012 --> 00:13:26.980
Yoga is not made, it takes place.

00:13:27.835 --> 00:13:32.293
which is living action in our evolution

00:13:32.689 --> 00:13:34.645
just as we became human beings

00:13:34.934 --> 00:13:39.044
you have not been turned into human being from a monkey

00:13:39.245 --> 00:13:40.650
you became so.

00:13:40.671 --> 00:13:44.593
the same way, from the state of a human being

00:13:44.794 --> 00:13:46.924
you go to a higher state.

00:13:47.219 --> 00:13:51.013
and to go that state you didn't have to work hard

00:13:51.388 --> 00:13:52.992
you didn't have to undergo any hardship

00:13:53.109 --> 00:13:56.309
You didnn't have to pay any money

00:13:56.510 --> 00:14:00.116
The main thing is that God doesn't understand money at all.

00:14:00.242 --> 00:14:02.079
What will He do after taking money?

00:14:02.344 --> 00:14:05.102
What is the need of offering money in His name?

00:14:05.543 --> 00:14:08.179
The person who values money most

00:14:08.258 --> 00:14:10.112
What is the use of giving money to him?

00:14:10.313 --> 00:14:12.147
For example, this land is earth

00:14:12.348 --> 00:14:14.955
put any seed into it, it will sprout on its own.

00:14:14.980 --> 00:14:16.787
The same way

00:14:16.988 --> 00:14:22.407
kundalini awakening takes place on its own in a sahaj way

00:14:23.924 --> 00:14:26.106
But such things people explain

00:14:26.307 --> 00:14:31.957
that for kundalini jagran you do this, you do that

00:14:32.020 --> 00:14:33.796
you give so much money,do this do that

