it is all false, absolutely false

00:14:36.486 --> 00:14:38.822
Do not trust such people at all

00:14:38.885 --> 00:14:43.105
And those who take money in the name of God, commit sin.

00:14:44.023 --> 00:14:45.592
They commit the greatest sin.

00:14:45.748 --> 00:14:47.910
And those who give, it will be said about you

00:14:48.111 --> 00:14:50.273
that your wisdom will be helpful.

