Another thing is that for this Sahaj

00:14:55.631 --> 00:14:58.349
because as I said that a seed

00:14:58.787 --> 00:15:00.872
by a living process only

00:15:00.994 --> 00:15:04.905
gets germinated, the same way it is a living process

00:15:05.243 --> 00:15:08.219
which is the work of living God.

