that pure desire is in the form of Mother

00:16:01.162 --> 00:16:04.653
is a power and when this power awakens

00:16:04.812 --> 00:16:11.554
then you witness the love of that all pervading power of God

00:16:11.892 --> 00:16:14.485
or we must say that we witness that power.

00:16:15.134 --> 00:16:18.344
That power you can feel inside you

00:16:18.545 --> 00:16:21.196
you can also see it on your head

00:16:21.397 --> 00:16:25.040
that cool breeze is coming out of your head

00:16:25.733 --> 00:16:27.631
as Adi shankaracharya ji has said,"SALEELAM SALEELEM."

00:16:28.359 --> 00:16:30.800
This way you can feel it in fingers as well

00:16:31.001 --> 00:16:32.609
although now a days

00:16:34.155 --> 00:16:38.146
it has opened for the whole world. It was not so earlier.

